doc.field: Ellsworth - the county seat and only city in Hancock County. Bar Harbor - on Mount Desert Island . Blue Hill Bucksport Castine Cranberry Isles Mount Desert Island - location of the Mt. Desert section of Acadia National Park . Orland Surry Trenton - location of the Hancock County-Bar Harbor Airport . Winter Harbor - home of the Schoodic Point section of Acadia National Park.
